INSTRUCTIONS FOR THE DEVELOPER (KAIYTHA SRINIDHI REDDY):

This file is a placeholder for your actual resume PDF.
To make the "Download Resume" button on your portfolio site work properly:
1. Export your latest resume/CV as a PDF named "resume.pdf".
2. Replace this file with your actual "resume.pdf" in the "public" folder of this project.
3. Once replaced, visitors clicking the "Download Resume" button will download your real PDF resume.
